  "text": "Coexistence of two different forms [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] in our sample might influence the results and conclusions of our study. Thus, we performed our analysis on two different datasets. One included both forms while the other included only WFTG/HD. The results revealed that there was excellent concordance between these two datasets (Table 3-5, Table S2 , S3, S4, Figure 2 ). This might be due to the low number of the WFTL/CM (n = 12) or the occurrence of hybridization between the two forms in China (see Discussion). Therefore we present the results of the whole datasets below.",
